{
  "id": "RAW_3b6b03",
  "title": "可惜，这个数据库技术又被别人领先一步......",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/qfRy82DBORtuixzUDUJKLQ",
  "date": "2025-02-07 16:06:22",
  "author": "liuxin",
  "siteName": "dbaplus社群",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"us-3745001\">\n    <section style=\"padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;\">\n     <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n      <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n       <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"us-4110356\">\n        <section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n         <section>\n          <span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: normal;\">10多年前，我还在IBM工作，内部有个特定的岗位叫做BA（Business Analyst），有点儿像现在的产品经理，就是负责和客户打交道，收集、分析客户需求，然后让程序员在系统中实现。</span>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">有一回我遇到了一个与众不同的老外BA，全名我忘了，名字以J开头，就叫她J姐吧。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">别的BA在测试系统时也就是在界面上操作，点来点去，看看对不对，而J姐不一样，在界面上点完后，一头扎进数据库，直接用SQL查看数据库的数据。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">然后提一个Bug：你这个表的数据不对啊，应该是这样这样的....</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">把我们都给整懵了，这太吓人了，程序员都没有活路了。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">后来，我在一个Java文件的开头注释中看到了J姐的大名，原来J姐程序员出身，这个系统的早期版本就是她写的，对代码和数据库比我们都熟。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">转眼10多年过去了，我再也没有遇到过像J姐这样的，一般的BA/产品经理是不懂代码和SQL，即使懂一些，也很难对系统底层有这么精深的理解。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n       </section>\n       <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">\n        <section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n         <section style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);padding-bottom:2px;text-align:center;\">\n          <section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);border-top-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);border-right-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);border-left-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);padding: 0.5em 1.5em;\">\n           <p style=\"line-height: 20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>一、更厉害的“J姐”</strong></span></p>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">最近，我发现一个更加强大、更加通用的“J姐”出现了。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Anthropic推出的MCP<strong>（Model Context Protocol）</strong> ，利用MCP，可以让各种AI助理用<strong>自然语言</strong>轻松地访问各种数据源，执行各种分析和查询。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">说概念没啥意思，看一个例子吧，使用Claude Desktop访问本地的SQLite数据库。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\">\n         <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;display:flex;\">\n          <section style=\"width: 0.6em;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;\">\n           <span style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);display:block;width:0.6em;opacity:0.2;height:0.6em;\" data-bgopacity=\"40%\"></span> <span style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 176, 240);display:block;width:0.6em;margin-top:2px;opacity:0.6;margin-bottom:2px;height:0.6em;\" data-bgopacity=\"25%\"></span> <span style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);display:block;width:0.6em;opacity:1;height:0.6em;\"></span>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;padding-left: 10px;\">\n           <section data-brushtype=\"text\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: #138bde;\"><strong>1. 让它连接上数据库：</strong></span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">直接用自然语言就行，连接完成以后，它还非常贴心地把数据库中的表都给读了出来。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"419\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144304\" data-ratio=\"0.737037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/12c77880-419a-48aa-6318-9d3a723c2b00/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/12c77880-419a-48aa-6318-9d3a723c2b00/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\">\n         <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;display:flex;\">\n          <section style=\"width: 0.6em;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;\">\n           <span style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);display:block;width:0.6em;opacity:0.2;height:0.6em;\" data-bgopacity=\"40%\"></span> <span style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 176, 240);display:block;width:0.6em;margin-top:2px;opacity:0.6;margin-bottom:2px;height:0.6em;\" data-bgopacity=\"25%\"></span> <span style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);display:block;width:0.6em;opacity:1;height:0.6em;\"></span>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;padding-left: 10px;\">\n           <section data-brushtype=\"text\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: #138bde;\"><strong>2. 查看产品表中有哪些产品和价格：</strong></span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"426\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144305\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/722a14e1-d55b-48c5-0320-586931e94a00/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/722a14e1-d55b-48c5-0320-586931e94a00/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\">\n         <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;display:flex;\">\n          <section style=\"width: 0.6em;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;\">\n           <span style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);display:block;width:0.6em;opacity:0.2;height:0.6em;\" data-bgopacity=\"40%\"></span> <span style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 176, 240);display:block;width:0.6em;margin-top:2px;opacity:0.6;margin-bottom:2px;height:0.6em;\" data-bgopacity=\"25%\"></span> <span style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);display:block;width:0.6em;opacity:1;height:0.6em;\"></span>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;padding-left: 10px;\">\n           <section data-brushtype=\"text\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: #138bde;\"><strong>3.计算一下平均价格</strong></span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"385\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144306\" data-ratio=\"0.6777777777777778\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c24f0e96-73ca-4caa-58af-ac02c7244800/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c24f0e96-73ca-4caa-58af-ac02c7244800/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\">\n         <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;display:flex;\">\n          <section style=\"width: 0.6em;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;\">\n           <span style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);display:block;width:0.6em;opacity:0.2;height:0.6em;\" data-bgopacity=\"40%\"></span> <span style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 176, 240);display:block;width:0.6em;margin-top:2px;opacity:0.6;margin-bottom:2px;height:0.6em;\" data-bgopacity=\"25%\"></span> <span style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);display:block;width:0.6em;opacity:1;height:0.6em;\"></span>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;padding-left: 10px;\">\n           <section data-brushtype=\"text\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: #138bde;\"><strong>4.分析一下价格分布，并且给出价格优化方案</strong></span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"413\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144307\" data-ratio=\"0.7268518518518519\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/715c5c73-a112-4b70-d8da-4e8848edde00/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/715c5c73-a112-4b70-d8da-4e8848edde00/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"412\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144308\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e125c05-3bfd-4df6-3e8a-8bc9529c3700/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e125c05-3bfd-4df6-3e8a-8bc9529c3700/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">是不是挺厉害的？可以这么说，有了MCP以后，你想要的任何SQL查询都可以通过自然语言来进行了。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n       </section>\n       <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">\n        <section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n         <section style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);padding-bottom:2px;text-align:center;\">\n          <section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);border-top-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);border-right-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);border-left-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);padding: 0.5em 1.5em;\">\n           <p style=\"line-height: 20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>二、这不就是Chat2DB吗？</strong></span></p>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">你可能觉得，这不就是Chat2DB吗？&nbsp;</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">还真不一样，Chat2DB是人家自己训练了一个大模型，实现自然语言到SQL的转换。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">这个MCP更像大模型一个通用的“外挂”，它是一种更具普遍性的协议，更加灵活，它可以支持各种数据源：数据库、文件、GitHub、Google Drive、Google Maps、Slack.....</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">它的架构是这样的，典型的Client/Server：</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"248\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144309\" data-ratio=\"0.4361111111111111\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d16a9586-39ca-4f1f-cfa9-6818c25e7e00/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d16a9586-39ca-4f1f-cfa9-6818c25e7e00/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">MCP Client</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">可以运行在Claude Desktop，Zed（代码编辑器当中）。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">MCP Server</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">其实就是对某一种数据源的封装，把这个数据源的能力给暴露出来，让Client去访问。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">例如对于SQLite，你就需要暴露出可以被访问的“函数”read_query，write_query等。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"157\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144310\" data-ratio=\"0.27685185185185185\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fb362d8c-a2a4-4d02-fc0b-f68b7dae6d00/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fb362d8c-a2a4-4d02-fc0b-f68b7dae6d00/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">当然，对于Server的每个操作，<strong>MCP协议都精确地定义了输入和输出</strong>，这样Client才可以理解它有哪些能力。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n         <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n          <li></li>\n         </ul>\n         <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"sql\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">types.Tool(</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    name=\"read_query\",</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    description=\"<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">Execute</span> a <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">query</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">on</span> the SQLite <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">database</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\",</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    inputSchema={</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">type</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">object</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\",</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        \"</span>properties<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": {</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">            \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">query</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": {\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">type</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">string</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\", \"</span>description<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">SQL</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">query</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">to</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">execute</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"},</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        },</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">required</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": [\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">query</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"],</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    },</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">),</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">types.Tool(</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    name=\"</span>write_query<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\",</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    description=\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">Execute</span> an <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">INSERT</span>, <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">UPDATE</span>, <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">or</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">DELETE</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">query</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">on</span> the SQLite <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">database</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\",</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    inputSchema={</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">type</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">object</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\",</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        \"</span>properties<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": {</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">            \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">query</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": {\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">type</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">string</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\", \"</span>description<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">SQL</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">query</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">to</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">execute</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"},</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        },</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        \"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">required</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\": [\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">query</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"],</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    },</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">),</span></code></pre>\n        </section>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">MCP Server 写好以后，需要在Claude中配置一下，告诉Claude，现在有这个数据源可以访问了。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"186\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144311\" data-ratio=\"0.32685185185185184\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62a724a1-fef0-4955-6b8f-fb6fb5e1c900/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62a724a1-fef0-4955-6b8f-fb6fb5e1c900/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">当你向Claude发出查询<strong>“产品表的平均价格是多少？”&nbsp;</strong> 执行流程是这样的：</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">(1) Claude利用大模型的能力把自然语言转化成需要执行的“函数”（read-query），交由MCP Server来执行。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">(2) MCP Server则把“函数”转化为SQL，交给SQLite数据库来执行。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"645\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144312\" data-ratio=\"1.1352757544224765\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/658f8de1-016a-4887-3164-3efbc5160000/public\" data-w=\"961\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/658f8de1-016a-4887-3164-3efbc5160000/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">SQLite是这样，其他数据源也是如此，官方已经推出了各种各样的MCP Server，可以直接使用：</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height:1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"495\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100144314\" data-ratio=\"0.8722222222222222\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b6fd08ba-5923-408b-b2ba-7008f6e50a00/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b6fd08ba-5923-408b-b2ba-7008f6e50a00/public\"></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n       </section>\n       <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">\n        <section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n         <section style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);padding-bottom:2px;text-align:center;\">\n          <section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);border-top-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);border-right-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);border-left-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);padding: 0.5em 1.5em;\">\n           <p style=\"line-height: 20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>三、美国人又领先了一步</strong></span></p>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">即使是最复杂最强大的大模型，也是被困在一个信息孤岛之中，和外界是隔离的。对每个数据源，都需要需要做“定制”，才能和大模型做连接。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Anthropic提出的这个MCP协议，其实就是避免大家重复造轮子，<strong>它就像电脑上的USB Type-C接口，</strong>给各种外围设备提供了一种标准的方式，让AI大模型可以轻松连接不同的数据源。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">当年的JDBC用统一的接口屏蔽了底层数据库的差异，让Java代码可以访问各种数据库，MCP也有点儿像。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">这个协议并不是只有Anthropic 的Claude 模型可以使用，<strong>任何大模型都可以使用，这很有可能打开一个全新的赛道。</strong></span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">MCP协议能不能做成，还依赖于OpenAI、谷歌、微软、Meta等AI巨头对它的接受度，以及是否愿意把它标准化，然后推广到整个业界。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">看到MCP，我的第一感觉就是：可惜可惜，美国人又领先了一步。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">MCP很难吗？并不难，这玩意儿正如它的名字所说<strong>Model Context Protocol</strong>，只是一个协议，只要能想到就能把它定义出来，然后一开源，有望成为一个重要标准。</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">它没有诞生在国内AI相关的公司，着实可惜啊！</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n        <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">全文完，觉得不错的话点个赞或者在看吧！</span></p>\n        <p><br></p>\n       </section>\n       <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n        <section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(19, 139, 213);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: red;visibility: visible;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">本文作者</span></strong></span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n        </section>\n        <section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <section label=\"Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved.\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 5px auto;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);line-height: 25.6px;visibility: visible;font-family: 微软雅黑;\">\n          <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-top: 5px;padding-bottom: 5px;outline: 0px;width: 100%;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\">\n           <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-bottom: 5px;padding-left: 20px;outline: 0px;border-left: 3px solid rgb(153, 153, 153);visibility: visible;\">\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">刘欣</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span>，</span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-decoration: inherit;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: red;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">著有畅销书《码农翻身》《半小时漫画计算机》，前IBM架构师，领导过多个企业应用架构设计和开发工作；洞</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">察技术本质，擅长用故事去讲解复杂技术。</span></span></span></span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\n        <section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 0.5em;padding-left: 0.5em;outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: left;\">\n          <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">来源丨公众号：<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">码农翻身</span>（ID：<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">coderising</span>）</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span>\n         </section>\n         <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 0.5em;padding-left: 0.5em;outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\n          <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">dbaplus社群欢迎广大技术人员投稿，投稿邮箱：</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">editor@dbaplus.cn</span></section></section></section></section></section></section></section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "MCP 协议通过标准化接口，使 AI 大模型能够更便捷地访问和利用各类数据源，加速 AI 应用开发。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "MCP 协议通过标准化接口，使 AI 大模型能够更便捷地访问和利用各类数据源，加速 AI 应用开发。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 Anthropic 公司推出的 MCP (Model Context Protocol) 协议，该协议旨在解决大模型与外部数据源连接的问题，降低数据集成的复杂性，提升大模型应用的效率。通过类比早期作者在 IBM 遇到的精通数据库的 BA “J 姐”，引出 MCP 作为更强大、更通用的解决方案。MCP 通过定义标准化的 Client/Server 架构，使得大模型可以使用自然语言访问各种数据源，如数据库、文件、云服务等。文章对比了 MCP 与 Chat2DB 的不同，强调 MCP 的通用性和灵活性。作者认为 MCP 类似于电脑的 USB Type-C 接口或 Java 的 JDBC，为 AI 大模型连接数据源提供了标准化的方式，有望成为行业重要标准，并推动 AI 生态发展，同时表达了对国内 AI 公司未率先推出此类协议的惋惜。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "MCP 协议为大模型连接各种数据源提供了标准化方案。",
      "explanation": "通过定义 Client/Server 架构和标准接口，简化了大模型访问不同数据源的流程，降低了开发和维护成本。"
    },
    {
      "point": "MCP 类似于 USB Type-C 接口，具有通用性和灵活性。",
      "explanation": "任何大模型都可以使用 MCP 协议连接不同的数据源，避免了重复造轮子，促进了生态系统的发展。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 巨头的支持和标准化推广将加速 MCP 协议的普及和应用。",
      "explanation": "OpenAI、谷歌、微软等公司的支持对于 MCP 成为行业标准至关重要，有助于推动其在整个业界的应用。"
    }
  ],
